OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMPs warn of 'fleecehold' on
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnew housing estates        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A group of MPs are calling on Housing  
OL,6, Secretary Michael Gove to ban new      
OL,7, so-called "fleecehold" estates in the  
OL,8, Leasehold Bill.                        
OL,10,FThe group is warning about leaseholders
OL,11,Fbeing stung with punishing bills for   
OL,12,Fprivate maintenance contracts.         
OL,14,FThese residents are locked into        
OL,15,Fcontracts where public amenities, such 
OL,16,Fas roads, are managed by an outside    
OL,17,Fcompany rather than the local council. 
OL,19,FUp to four million people are now      
OL,20,Fthought to be living on such estates.  
